cosmetica.offline.message: We couldn't connect to Cosmetica servers! This could be because you have an issue with or a slow internet connection, or there was an error at startup.
cosmetica.unauthenticated.message: We couldn't authenticate your account! This could be because you're using a cracked Minecraft account or your internet isn't working.
cosmetica.rsewarning.title: Do you want to enable Region-Specific Effects?
cosmetica.rsewarning.description1: If you choose 'yes,' people will be able to see your region-specific cosmetics
cosmetica.rsewarning.description2: and may use them to determine your country of origin.
cosmetica.rsewarning.description3: You will also be able to see the region-specific cosmetics of others.
